{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, this noising and denoising procedure does not model any biophysical processes of protein folding.",
    "FoldingDiff trains such a diffusion model to generate new protein backbone structures using our angular formulation.",
    "Since our diffusion model acts upon periodic angular values, we ensure that noising and denoising procedures are wrapped about the domain ½Àπ,πÞ.",
    "We formulate the denoising model p with a bidirectional transformer model and set T = 1000 noising steps.",
    "Notably, this transformer architecture does not provide rotation or translation equivariance, as our input representation itself is intrinsically rotation-and translationinvariant."
  ]
}